title: Google keeping its place atop the AI rankings might mean doing something it's resisting
full_text:
Google keeping its place atop the AI rankings might mean doing something it's resisting. As Google's earnings report looms, its AI strategy and ad business with Gemini 3 put it at the forefront of a volatile AI market.. Google CEO Sundar Pichai.CAMILLE COHEN/AFP via Getty Images
